branchCategory.name: TIRS
branchCategory.description: <p>Flame resistant TIRS soft nylon tubing (Equivalent to UL-94 Standard V-0), is available in 20 and 100 meter rolls. The TIRS series is applicable for general air pressure and water in a spark atmosphere such as spot welding. Available colors include black, white, red, blue and green.</p>
